{"tid":313281,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"謝 婷 婷：鷹 眼 問 我 為 何 不 承 認 其 男 友 身 份","createTime":"2017-07-08T07:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T04:24:53.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":95,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d6ce5e10eac6a4592f19765ed5af2e0cf2ff883","tid":313281,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"謝婷婷上月高調默認與「鷹眼」謝洛美維拿（Jeremy Renner）拍拖，惟之後男方傳有正印女友，日前婷婷再改口指兩人沒真正拍拖。<br />\n<br />\n婷婷前晚出席品牌活動，問到鷹眼近日手部受傷時，她卻以曖昧關係形容兩人的感情狀況，究竟二人是甚麼關係？婷婷笑言：「同鷹眼嘅關係冇改變，不過見大家咁關心我哋嘅狀況，所以今日都有text佢，問吓佢隻手傷成點，佢話仲係好痛。」她直言享受這種曖昧關係，又透露鷹眼兩次問她為何不承認其「男友」身份，婷婷續笑道：「其實英文有好多種，見到隻狗可以係I love you，小朋友同好友都可以係I love you，唔會無啦啦未得對方承認之下，去認呢個男友身份同關係！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170708/large/08ec3p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170708%2Flarge%2F08ec3p11.jpg&h=3cc63eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n謝婷婷形容自己跟鷹眼關係是曖昧。"},{"pid":"beb9a00fb5c6b2965b940ddbf2ce41ada38d35ed","tid":313281,"uid":14497,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"臭閪"},{"pid":"aa4da6d0f5d20b97b1efce6df015bef086850d4b","tid":313281,"uid":3482,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"好撚樣衰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1c767a998c512027be4bb9e648d230911ac171","tid":313281,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"WHO?"},{"pid":"cf2b148aba563d66b2edcbf9c8a6a6ad14094bf7","tid":313281,"uid":96877,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"煩撚過西班牙老公"},{"pid":"aebaf034e23a322667f0fb1af7b909854c6bf3d0","tid":313281,"uid":28845,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"cit